77
00:07:58,265 --> 00:07:59,432
Tens a certeza?

78
00:07:59,500 --> 00:08:00,333
Não.

79
00:08:01,502 --> 00:08:02,535
O que quer isso dizer?

80
00:08:03,904 --> 00:08:05,872
